Our preoccupation at this point in the @OfficialPDPNig should not focus on elections, but on rebuilding and strengthening our party for the challenges ahead of us. -AA Alhaji Atiku Abubakar has advised the  Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) to focus rebuilding the party and not the elections, t The PDP presidential candidate in on his Twitter handle tweeted:  “Our preoccupation at this point in the @OfficialPDPNig should not focus on elections, but on rebuilding and strengthening our party for the challenges ahead of us,”